snippet.title: The Sims 4 Spa Day: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Treat your Sims to a day of pampering with The Sims 4 Spa Day!
 
Learn more about this Game Pack: http://o.ea.com/40382
 
Take your Sims to the spa for a revitalizing massage or work on the all-new Wellness skill with some yoga. Choose from 4 pre-built venues, build one of your very own, or bring all the tranquility into your Sim’s home with all-new objects and furnishings.
